OL,6,FA nurse who started her first job at
OL,7,FJersey's General Hospital aged just 17
OL,8,Fhas now retired after working there
OL,9,Ffor 48 years.
OL,11,FWendy Baugh spent her whole career at
OL,12,Fthe island's hospital, helping many
OL,13,Fthousands of patients and climbing the
OL,14,Fcareer ladder to Senior Nurse
OL,15,FPractitioner.
OL,17,FDespite her decades of service looking
OL,18,Fafter others, Wendy says it is a job
OL,19,Fshe rather fell into at the start.
