OL,3,CNurse leaves her first job after 48
OL,4,Cyears to retire
OL,6,FShe explains: "I only went into it
OL,7,Fbecause my friend Linda wanted to.
OL,9,F"My father said, 'Oh, I think you
OL,10,Fshould go into finance, you'd have a
OL,11,Fjob for life'."
OL,13,FBut that is exactly what Wendy ended
OL,14,Fup with in healthcare and her career
OL,15,Fwas celebrated by colleagues at a
OL,16,Fleaving party in the hospital this
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,19,FWendy adds: "I have no regrets
OL,20,Fwhatsoever. It's a career that I've
OL,21,Floved right the way through.
