OL,3,CNurse leaves her first job after 48
OL,4,Cyears to retire
OL,6,F"The patients never fail to amaze me,
OL,7,Fthe resilience of some people, you see
OL,8,Fwhat they've been through and then
OL,9,Fthey get up and walk home, you think,
OL,10,F'Wow'.
OL,12,F"It is the most rewarding career,
OL,13,Fdefinitely."
OL,15,FMany paid tribute to Wendy's kind
OL,16,Fnature and the impact she has had
OL,17,Fthroughout her time as a nurse.
